title: The Green Bean Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Juice bar, Take-out, Catering
description: Casual neighborhood veggie cafe with an extensive juices and food menu. Offers main entrees, sandwiches, pizza, smoothies, desserts, all-day breakfast, vegan sweets, and some raw food. Seating is available for both table and counter service.
